      <c01 level="series">
        <did>
          <unittitle>Subject File</unittitle>
        </did>
        <scopecontent>
          <p>The subject file, like the correspondence, deals primarily with the St. Lawrence Seaway and the American Concrete Institute. The seaway material includes a large number of newspaper clippings and supportive material dating back to the 1920's. The ACI material is strongest regarding committee 711, dealing with precast floor systems. The subject file reflects Menefee's opinion on immigration policy in the 1920s, prohibition, and prayer in public schools. It also contains a quantity of material about various water diversion projects.</p>
        </scopecontent>
